Bintang Emas.

185
00:23:36,319 --> 00:23:38,977
Sungguh?
/ Ya.

186
00:23:39,115 --> 00:23:41,290
Cunnilingus masih dihitung?

187
00:23:41,428 --> 00:23:43,154
Ya.
/ Sayang sekali.

188
